text: Camille Thomasina Schrier (born June 30, 1995) is an American beauty pageant contestant. She won the 2020 Miss America. In June 2019, she was crowned Miss Virginia 2019. Schrier began competing in pageants at age 14. Schrier represented Virginia at the 2020 Miss America Pageants. ==References== Category:Miss America winners Category:1995 births Category:Living people Category:Models from Pennsylvania Category:People from Blacksburg, Virginia
